title: The Halloween Candy Draft + Morgan2 Asks Door-to-Doors Salesman on a Date + Jake Owen on Watching his New Movie
itunes:title: The Halloween Candy Draft + Morgan2 Asks Door-to-Doors Salesman on a Date + Jake Owen on Watching his New Movie
description:
We do our Fantasy Draft on favorite Halloween Candy. Morgan2 gives us an update on the salesman who came to her house that she thought was cute…she asked him out on a date! We talk to Jake Owen about Cher tweeting him, his movie premiere and an update on his family.
